    {
      "id": "l9-phrases",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Polite phrases",
      "body": "# Polite phrases\n\nLonger phrases for everyday courtesy:\n\n| English | Hindi |\n|---|---|\n| Can you help me? | क्या आप मेरी मदद कर सकते हैं? |\n| After you. | आप पहले। |\n| Take care. | अपना ख़्याल रखना। |\n| Pleased to meet you. | आपसे मिलकर ख़ुशी हुई। |\n\nThe word **can** here makes a request polite: *Can you help me?* is softer than *Help me*. Add **please** for extra courtesy: *Can you help me, please?*"
    },
